OL,7,FIt's been revealed Swindon's Oasis
OL,8,Fleisure centre will take 18 months to
OL,9,Frefurbish once the planning
OL,10,Fapplication is approved.
OL,12,FDamien Siviter, the chief executive of
OL,13,FSeven Capital, which holds a 99-year
OL,14,Flease on the building, was at the
OL,15,Fmeeting of Swindon Borough Council's
OL,16,FBuild a Better Swindon policy
OL,17,Fcommittee.
