OL,7,FHe revealed it will take about 18
OL,8,Fmonths from the planning application
OL,9,Fto refurbish the Oasis leisure centre
OL,10,Fbeing approved, to re-opening the
OL,11,Fcentre again.
OL,13,FThis means the planning consent should
OL,14,Fbe given within the next three to four
OL,15,Fmonths if there is any hope of having
OL,16,Fit opened again in 2026 ` the 50th
OL,17,Fanniversary of its original opening.
