OL,7,FWhile he was there to talk about the
OL,8,Fcompany's plans for the centre, which
OL,9,Fhas been shut since late 2020, he
OL,10,Fwasn't able to answer questions
OL,11,Fspecifically about the planning
OL,12,Fapplication.
OL,14,FCouncillor Stanka Adamcova referred to
OL,15,Fthe previously expressed ambition of
OL,16,FSeven Capital to have the centre open
OL,17,Fagain in 2026, and asked whether that
OL,18,Fwas achievable.
