OL,4,Cmonths to refurbish once planning is
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FMr Siviter said: "We all have to have
OL,8,Fa goal. It will broadly take 18 months
OL,9,Ffrom planning approval, so it is
OL,10,Fpossible."
OL,12,FCllr Adamcova asked what the main
OL,13,Frisks to that were. Mr Siviter said:
OL,14,F"There are three: the operator, the
OL,15,Fcontractor and finance."
OL,17,FHe said that the company was close to
OL,18,Fagreeing a lease with its preferred
OL,19,Foperator.
