OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FMr Siviter said finance was being
OL,8,Fhandled by Seven Capital itself, and
OL,9,Fthere was no debt on the centre at
OL,10,Fall, so no third parties needed to be
OL,11,Fasked. But a contractor could not be
OL,12,Fappointed until planning consent was
OL,13,Fgranted.
OL,15,FCouncil Dan Adams asked when a
OL,16,Fdetailed application for the pool, and
OL,17,Fnot just the dome and dry-side of the
OL,18,Fcentre, would be coming.
