OL,4,Cmonths to refurbish once planning is
OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,FMr Siviter said it would be soon: "We
OL,8,Fwanted to wait until after the public
OL,9,Fengagement. And we have fed that back
OL,10,Fto the operator, discussing wave
OL,11,Fmachines and the slides.
OL,13,F"I think people will see how far we've
OL,14,Fmoved from our original thinking to
OL,15,Faccommodate that feedback we received."
OL,17,FThe company's applications to
OL,18,Frefurbish the centre, and to build 700
OL,19,Fflats on the site as the way to
OL,20,Ffinance the refurbishment, have not
OL,21,Fyet been decided.
